text: Patrick Fitzgerald (born 1960) is the former United States Attorney for the Northern District of Illinois. Patrick Fitzgerald may also refer to: *Patrik Fitzgerald (born 1956), British singer-songwriter *Pat Fitzgerald (born 1974), football coach *Patrick Fitzgerald (Irish judge), fourteenth century judge *Patrick Fitzgerald (1882–1965), actor, better known as Creighton Hale ==See also== *Pat Fitzgerald (disambiguation)
